GeliShell — Gerisabet Ecosystem
===============================

GeliShell is a cross-platform shell REPL with canonical command
translation, security guardrails, and an integrated AI assistant.

It is part of the Gerisabet ecosystem:

  • Gerisabet-AI        — Desktop RAG/chat application (Tauri v2 + React 19)
  • GeliShell           — Shell REPL with translation and guardrails (Rust)
  • Gerisabet.Gateway   — Centralized API Gateway (ASP.NET Core 10)

